name: Sketchsketch
body:
### Sketchsketch
This is work-in-progress drawing tool that allows undo/redo history, animated playback of your drawing, and export to animated .gif via the use of a web worker.

### Authors and Contributors
Developed as a fun side-project by Zak Nitsch (@ZedLove).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
